Jim?

189
00:19:54.393 --> 00:19:55.940
Jim.

190
00:19:59.607 --> 00:20:01.530
Are you all right?

191
00:20:03.110 --> 00:20:04.703
Yeah.

192
00:20:06.238 --> 00:20:08.616
I thought I heard a child crying.

193
00:20:11.786 --> 00:20:15.040
It was... It was me.

194
00:20:17.124 --> 00:20:21.129
Why don't you come on inside?
I'll fix you a cup of coffee.


195
00:20:22.463 --> 00:20:24.056
Yeah.

196
00:20:24.840 --> 00:20:26.888
In a minute.

197
00:20:41.107 --> 00:20:43.109
Run, Jimmy, run!

