199
00:21:20.604 --> 00:21:22.572
Well, maybe the message will
get through to you, Chip!


200
00:21:22.648 --> 00:21:25.117
You get an F on your midterm,
the Coach is gonna cut you from the team.


201
00:21:25.192 --> 00:21:26.944
If you give me one more F,
I swear to God, I'm gonna...


202
00:21:27.027 --> 00:21:28.904
Hey, hey, hey, hey!

203
00:21:29.697 --> 00:21:33.668
Look, Chip, I played football, too,
and I did my school work.


204
00:21:33.743 --> 00:21:38.214
Now, you're a smart guy.
You wanna play, just do the work.


205
00:21:40.708 --> 00:21:43.302
You gonna take that, dude?

206
00:21:55.890 --> 00:21:57.892
You're dead, man!

207
00:21:57.975 --> 00:21:59.568
You.

208
00:22:02.021 --> 00:22:04.274
Come on. Come on.

209
00:22:19.580 --> 00:22:22.504
What were you and Chip talking about?
He looked pretty mad.


210
00:22:22.583 --> 00:22:26.087
Oh, no, no, we...
We were just talking.


211
00:22:30.591 --> 00:22:32.559
What is it?

212
00:22:37.973 --> 00:22:42.570
I don't know. Mr. Norman, Jim...

213
00:22:43.604 --> 00:22:47.325
You know how you're saying
that history repeats itself?


214
00:22:47.399 --> 00:22:52.200
I've been thinking a lot about that,
and that really bothers me.


215
00:22:52.279 --> 00:22:55.078
- Why is that?
- I don't know.


216
00:22:55.157 --> 00:22:58.536
