218
00:23:02.957 --> 00:23:05.130
I think that's what makes
a person great is...


219
00:23:05.209 --> 00:23:09.134
guts and the ability to
change the patterns.


220
00:23:10.256 --> 00:23:14.762
I was listening to that "Dust
in the Wind" song last night.


221
00:23:14.844 --> 00:23:16.346
