of dust in someone's eye, you know?


223
00:23:22.226 --> 00:23:24.570
Well, I don't think that's
all you'll be, Billy.


224
00:23:24.645 --> 00:23:27.819
'Cause, you're learning how to think.
That's a good sign.


225
00:23:37.449 --> 00:23:41.124
Hey, do I get extra
credit for thinking?


226
00:23:55.885 --> 00:23:59.355
Billy? Your wallet! Billy?

