00:24:55.235 --> 00:24:56.031
Come on!

229
00:25:00.491 --> 00:25:01.538
Hey.

230
00:25:04.119 --> 00:25:04.790
Hey!

231
00:25:10.668 --> 00:25:12.261
Come on!

232
00:25:12.711 --> 00:25:14.258
Stop!

233
00:25:16.048 --> 00:25:18.346
What are you guys doing?

234
00:25:18.425 --> 00:25:20.974
Help me! Help me!

235
00:25:22.137 --> 00:25:23.935
Help me!

236
00:25:28.310 --> 00:25:31.280
Billy! Billy!

237
00:25:47.705 --> 00:25:49.298
